    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>两个阵营。一场残酷的战争。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《<i>Men of War: Vietnam</i>》将这款备受赞誉的即时战术系列带入全新的战区——1968年的东南亚丛林。两条剧情战役将揭示冲突双方的经历，让你身临其境感受越南战争的混乱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/63940/extras/82752f533f944b1aff4ffdeee718a8b3.poster.avif?t=1768394224\" width=1170 height=518 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/63940/extras/82752f533f944b1aff4ffdeee718a8b3.webm?t=1768394224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/63940/extras/82752f533f944b1aff4ffdeee718a8b3.mp4?t=1768394224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在美军战役中，你将指挥一支精锐特种部队——中士 John Merrill、机枪手 Jim Walsh、狙击手 Sonny Armstrong、掷弹兵 Carl Dillan 和工兵 Bill Kirby。每个任务都让他们陷入绝境：深入敌后、失去增援，只能依靠技能、勇气和彼此生存。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >北越战役讲述的是另一段故事——关于生存与毅力。两名苏联顾问与两名北越士兵在埋伏中幸存下来，他们必须在春节攻势的混乱中穿越敌军领地，途经柬埔寨、老挝和湄公河三角洲，艰难返回基地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/63940/extras/84b660647162b003e5cc41ff6078ac28.poster.avif?t=1768394224\" width=1170 height=518 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/63940/extras/84b660647162b003e5cc41ff6078ac28.webm?t=1768394224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/63940/extras/84b660647162b003e5cc41ff6078ac28.mp4?t=1768394224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >任务类型多样，包括潜行行动、营救任务、大规模突袭、伏击和绝望的防御战。茂密的丛林、狭窄的小道和泥泞的河流既是盟友，也是敌人，考验着你的每一个战术直觉。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/63940/extras/991314785f0eea8b1d33ce3d3ece6301.poster.avif?t=1768394224\" width=1170 height=518 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/63940/extras/991314785f0eea8b1d33ce3d3ece6301.webm?t=1768394224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/63940/extras/991314785f0eea8b1d33ce3d3ece6301.mp4?t=1768394224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >功能</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>双线剧情战役</strong>——从美军特种部队和北越军队的双重视角体验战争。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>真实战斗场景</strong>——胡志明小道伏击、深入老挝和柬埔寨突袭、桥梁防御以及春节攻势期间的城市战。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>新时代，新武器</strong>——使用标志性武器如 M16、AK-47、RPG-2、M60、M72 LAW，并指挥 T-54、M113、Patton III 等载具。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>4 人合作模式</strong>——与好友一起完成任务。受 GameSpy 于 5 月 31 日关闭影响，在线服务终止，但仍可通过 LAN、DirectIP 和 GameRanger 进行游戏。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>电影般的氛围</strong>——摇滚广播、丛林上空的“休伊”直升机与 1968 年的酷热。</p></li></ul>",
